cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Agentic Governance & Security Controls"
message: "If you use this standard, please cite it."
type: dataset
authors:
  - name: "COHUMAIN Labs"
  - name: "SafeAlign AI"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2026-01-01
license: CC-BY-4.0
url: "https://github.com/HimJoe/Agentic-governance-and-security-controls-by-COHUMAIN-Labs-and-Safealign-AI"
abstract: >
  An open, vendor-neutral control standard unifying governance and security for
  agentic and generative AI systems. Twenty-five controls across four pillars
  (Safety, Alignment, Governance, Security), each risk-justified and mapped to the
  MIT AI Risk Repository, MITRE ATLAS, MITRE ATT&CK, and the EU AI Act, NIST AI RMF
  and ISO/IEC 42001.
keywords:
  - agentic AI
  - AI governance
  - AI security
  - AI risk
  - MITRE ATLAS
  - MIT AI Risk Repository
  - EU AI Act
